strings:
<voice_0x01001417><center>That's all I can do.
<center>No one can walk into the ham unnoticed.

<voice_0x01001418><center>But the mountains are full of caves.
<center>You should be able to make it
<center>to the top of the hill.

<voice_0x01001419><center>If you want to return to the mountains,
<center>call me and I'll take you home.

<voice_0x0100141A><center>Until we meet again.
<center>Hold my ball,
<center>you are my only hope
